- Nechaj to tak, Dong Min.

64
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:16,280
Ja... dal som mu tú injekciu.

65
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:18,240
Ale stále nič nepovedal.

66
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,810
Prečo nič nehovorí?

67
00:06:19,820 --> 00:06:22,020
Ste si istý, že to bolo sérum pravdy?

68
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:24,660
Prečo by som ti veril ohľadom
toho séra, ty bastard?

69
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,510
- Ty bastard!
- Prestaň, Dong Min!

70
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:29,920
- Pomysli na Jae Yula a kašli na to.
- Ak to nebolo sérum, tak čo potom?

71
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,690
